Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.90,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}sono hitomi ni utsutteiru no wa
