Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.78,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}real sore tomo nijigen
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.78,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Reality or something 2-D?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.78,0:21:09.37,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}tayasuku kawaii da nante iwanai de yo ne
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.78,0:21:09.37,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Don't just say I look pretty like it's no big deal to me
Dialogue: 2,0:21:09.37,0:21:15.71,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}ashita mo me wo kosutte ohayou wo itte
Dialogue: 2,0:21:09.37,0:21:15.71,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Tomorrow, you'll rub your eyes and say "good morning"
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.71,0:21:22.59,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}tawai mo nai koto takusan oshiete
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.71,0:21:22.59,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}And talk about all sorts of pointless stuff
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.59,0:21:29.14,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}sukoshizutsu chikadzuiteku kyori ni
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.59,0:21:29.14,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}And as we slowly grow closer together
Dialogue: 2,0:21:29.14,0:21:35.19,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}doushiyou jibun ja nai mitai da
Dialogue: 2,0:21:29.14,0:21:35.19,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}What do I do? What am I usually like?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.52,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}merry-go-round ga tomaranakute
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.52,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}This merry-go-round just never stops
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.52,0:21:45.32,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}mawaru mawaru keshiki ga kawatteku
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.52,0:21:45.32,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Spinning, spinning, the scenery blurs by
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.32,0:21:48.32,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}colorful na yume wo miru
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.32,0:21:48.32,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Like a colorful dream
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.24,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}dokudoku shite karadajuu wo
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.24,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Throb, throb, I can feel them inside
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.96,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}meguru meguru kimochi
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.96,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Going 'round and 'round, these feelings
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.96,0:22:00.00,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}mada kotoba ni dekinakute
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.96,0:22:00.00,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}I still can't put them into words
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.00,0:22:04.42,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}hitokoto sore de juubun nanoni
